        <h2 class="text-center">What We Do</h2>
        <h4 class="text-center">Video/POS Cloud Integration</h4>
        <p>Having more than 70 years of security video experience between them, Phil Tolle and Kevin Searight have co-founded <strong>3 Palms Intelligent Video Solutions</strong> to support the loss prevention practices of small and midsize multi-site businesses with their Point of Sale transactions.</p>
        <p>With our focus on cloud base security solutions, 3 Palms provides the <strong>Solink Corp.</strong> Network Appliance solution to integrate Existing Video with Point of Sale data and detail. Supported by a forensic case management suite, our Clients have access to both local and centralized cloud based archive storage for Loss Prevention investigations and video/data review in the web and mobile app. Health monitoring options identify, notify, and minimize the downtime of your current Video system investment while online 24/7 chat support is always available. The Network Appliance device can either be installed parallel to your existing Video infrastructure so that no expensive physical hardware/software re-configurations are required to your NVR server device, or as a standalone recording solution. The only connectivity required is to an open port on the PoE / Encoder switch and a static IP Address on your network.</p>
        <p>The support and partnership of multiple Video Manufacturers affords 3 Palms the ability to provide our Clients with a cost-effective option to supplement and support their existing video investment.</p>
    </div>
